scene.message:
Yukino: This is... the{nl}
fencing club room...{nl}
which mea{wait_fr:30}ns{wait_fr:30}...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: These two's dream...{nl}
In reality they only fought,{waitkey}{clearbox}but I see - a fine example{nl}
of "the more they quarrel,{nl}
the closer they are."{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Gah! I'm in total{nl}
shock!{waitkey}{clearbox}Tamaki actually liked that{nl}
Tadashi guy?! Somebody{nl}
tell me it's a dream!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Wait, this IS a dream??{nl}
Huh? Is this real and{nl}
that a dream, or...?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: No way!{nl}
So these two really were{nl}
that kind of couple after all.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: I've no intention of{nl}
speaking ill of these two,{nl}
but I can't bear to watch...{waitkey}in various senses...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Th-they look so{nl}
very happy... It feels{nl}
almost wrong to{waitkey}call out to them.{waitkey}{ret}

Tadashi: See,{nl}
you can see yourself{nl}
in my eyes, right?{waitkey}{clearbox}And in your eyes,{nl}
I can see myself...{nl}
Ahh, we are one!{waitkey}{ret}

Tamaki: Ahh,{nl}
Tadashi is there{nl}
in my eyes♥{waitkey}{clearbox}Ahh, in Tadashi's eyes{nl}
I can see myself...{nl}
We've become one!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: ...............{nl}
Phew... let's have them{nl}
continue after they wake.{waitkey}Let's just wake them up.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Being in someone{nl}
else's dream really is{nl}
uncomfortable, no matter what.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: So those two had a{nl}
flavonoid kind of thing{nl}
going. So enviable~{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: "A 'no, no' can still{nl}
mean 'yes,'" hm.{nl}
Curious things, men and women.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Kuhh...{nl}
Please! Leave heartbroken,{nl}
dumped me alone{waitkey}{clearbox}for a while, would you...{nl}
Ahh... Tamaki...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Looking at this club{nl}
room, you'd never imagine this{nl}
is the "Anti-Dream World."{waitkey}{clearbox}Unthinkable, really.{waitkey}{ret}

Tadashi: Ahh! Ahh!{nl}
So noisy! And it was just{nl}
getting good!{waitkey}{clearbox}What a rude person{nl}
you are!{waitkey}{ret}

Tamaki: How noisy.{nl}
Interrupt us and I won't{nl}
forgive you!{waitkey}{ret}
